{"tid":528340,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[高質女神盡在連登]第十八輪LIHKG 香港乙組女神聯賽17/18投選專區 #湯洛雯 #王敏奕 #朱智賢 #陳潔玲 #賴慰玲 #蘇麗珊","createTime":"2018-01-13T16:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T16:34:45.000Z","uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"813c15217268908a4fda51d6c9db69ed4b072085","tid":528340,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:30am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n蔡思貝v歐鎧淳<br />\n王敏奕v周慧敏<br />\n胡琳v駱文捷<br />\n黃德藍v湯洛雯<br />\n陳潔玲v勞嘉怡<br />\n朱智賢v賴慰玲<br />\n陳婉婷v陳寶珊<br />\n何雁詩v蘇麗珊<br />\n林映蔚v菊梓喬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乙組第十七輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qF2shI5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqF2shI5.png&h=664f64d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=DAvTgABvU1htLMBbKnqBP8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cd0bad91\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2b6741faacdbdde9edeb3e7111be9a58e72732","tid":528340,"uid":92376,"like":78,"dislike":52,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽第十八輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-1-14 12:30am-10:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Vj0QbVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVj0QbVW.png&h=237c56e9&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OcxgLD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOcxgLD7.png&h=99f42653&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(14)蔡思貝vs歐鎧淳(15)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"4529700cde95a1581182c257f0e04213ff012cb5","tid":528340,"uid":92376,"like":134,"dislike":22,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-1-14 12:32am-10:32pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gcM73jk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgcM73jk.png&h=dc05bd20&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HScnebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHScnebc.png&h=6e4838c4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(2)王敏奕vs周慧敏(10)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"36ded7e1a75b55b1ec82482773a387167196f098","tid":528340,"uid":92376,"like":84,"dislike":35,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyT